java.lang.Object
net.minecraft.world.entity.ai.behavior.Behavior<E extends net.minecraft.world.entity.LivingEntity>

BehaviorControl<E>
public abstract class Behavior<E extends net.minecraft.world.entity.LivingEntity>  extends Object implements BehaviorControl<E>
Represents a Behavior that can be ran.
